      "content": "it's just so exhausting. every day is just more of the same emptiness. i look at my life and i just see a massive hole where my heart used to be. i don't want \"hope\" or \"help,\" i just want the weight to stop. i want to find some kind of peace. it feels like the only way to actually get that peace is to just... stop everything. to finally be still.",
